OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry although fairly cloudy.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will remain
OL,8,Fdry but with a good deal of cloud at
OL,9,Ftimes. Light northeasterly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FStaying dry with cloud
OL,12,Fthinning to allow some bright or sunny
OL,13,Fintervals by afternoon. Light winds.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,16,FLittle change. Remaining dry with
OL,17,Fvariable amounts of cloud and some
OL,18,Fsunny periods. Light winds.
